The goal is simple - have more points than your opponent
while being under 22. Scoring over 21 points is immediate
defeat even if your opponent has fewer points.
The game starts with your opponent drawing their first card.
You will get 2 cards for a start. Scoring 21 points with them
will win you the round at once.

If you got a third card and your total score is less than 22,

until you’ll get 5 cards or get over 21 points.
After holding, the initiative goes to your opponent. They

Good luck and don’t be greedy on the draw!
